"title": "8491: watchfulness, divine",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8491",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The Lord's alertness to the needs of his people, his constant care for them and his awareness of the power and evil intent of their enemies.</p>\n<h2>The Lord's watchfulness over his people in danger or trouble</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps121:1-Ps121:8\">PSA 121:1–121:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:16\">EXO 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:9-Deut32:10\">DEU 32:9–32:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra5:5\">EZR 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:6\">PSA 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps11:4-Ps11:5\">PSA 11:4–11:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:8\">PSA 17:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:6\">PSA 32:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:16-Ps33:18\">PSA 33:16–33:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:7\">PSA 34:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:1\">PSA 127:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:20\">PSA 145:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:8\">ZEC 9:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech12:4\">ZEC 12:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:29-Matt10:31\">MAT 10:29–10:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:1-John10:9\">JHN 10:1–10:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:12\">2TI 1:12</a></p>\n<h2>The Lord's watchfulness means that his people's needs are met</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:9\">PSA 146:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:15\">GEN 28:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:15\">GEN 48:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut2:7\">DEU 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:12\">DEU 11:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:9\">2CH 16:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:12\">JOB 10:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job29:2\">JOB 29:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer24:6\">JER 24:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:28\">JER 31:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:18\">DAN 9:18</a></p>\n<h3>The watchfulness of a shepherd</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:1\">PSA 23:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:9\">PSA 28:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:11\">ISA 40:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:6\">MAT 2:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:1-John10:9\">JHN 10:1–10:9</a></p>\n<h2>The Lord's watchfulness means that he hears his people's prayers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:15\">PSA 34:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:28-1Kgs8:30\">1KI 8:28–8:30</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:20\">2CH 6:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:3\">1KI 9:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:16\">2CH 7:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:6\">NEH 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:12\">1PE 3:12</a></p>\n<h2>The Lord's watchfulness with a view to correction</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:25-Jer7:26\">JER 7:25–7:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:13\">JER 7:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:7\">JER 11:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:4\">JER 25:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:33\">JER 32:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:28\">2SA 22:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:11\">JOB 33:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer16:16-Jer16:17\">JER 16:16–16:17</a></p>\n<h2>The Lord's watchfulness in seeking out those who have gone astray</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:16\">EZK 34:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:12\">MAT 18:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:4\">LUK 15:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:25\">1PE 2:25</a></p>\n<h2>People are vulnerable without the Lord's watchfulness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:36\">MAT 9:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:17\">1KI 22:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr18:16\">2CH 18:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:14\">ISA 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:11-Ezek34:12\">EZK 34:11–34:12</a></p>",
